<div class="bg-light rounded h-100 p-5">
  <h1>Ember Bootstrap Modals Manager</h1>
  <p class="fw-light fs-4">Ember-addon that provides a simple mechanism for
    interaction with user using modals.</p>
  <p>This addon is based on modals from
    <a
      target="_blank"
      href="https://www.ember-bootstrap.com/"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
    >ember-bootstrap</a>.</p>

